6 - Marketing Data Mart 6

A Data Mart is a subset of a data warehouse oriented to a specific business line. Data marts contain repositories of summarized data collected for analysis on a specific section or unit within an organization, in this case, the marketing department.

1. Download the MarketingDataMart.zip included above

2. Extract file to a location of your choice and save the MarketingDataMart.sql file in your "Downloads" folder

3. Open SQL Server Management Studios. After entering your login credentials, go to the object explorer, right click "Database" and click "New Database"



4. Name the database "DataWarehouse" and then click "OK"



5. Click "open folder"




6. Go to your "Downloads" file and select the "Marketing Data Mart" file. Open the SQL File. It should look like the below picture. 



7. Click "Execute" or press F5 to run the script. 



Congratulations, your data mart is now populated with data!
